  "detailed_description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/fdb519eab434ceb0aeb905190b94b2bc.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/fdb519eab434ceb0aeb905190b94b2bc.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/fdb519eab434ceb0aeb905190b94b2bc.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to Tether, a world where chalk bags have arms and everything colorful is your personal playground. Its physics-driven movement system lets you play your way. Whether you like daring jumps, strategic climbs, or spinning in endless circles, the choice is yours!<br><br><br><strong>GRAB, CLIMB, SWING</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/a5ec056adff81c966a5fb284869e59e9.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/a5ec056adff81c966a5fb284869e59e9.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/a5ec056adff81c966a5fb284869e59e9.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tether isn’t your typical 2D platformer. There’s no running and jumping. Instead, master the art of grabbing, swinging, and flinging and climb your way to the top!<br><br><br><strong>EXPLORE WITH FRIENDS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/1134b04f399341e9f63cb9dedd738b15.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/1134b04f399341e9f63cb9dedd738b15.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/1134b04f399341e9f63cb9dedd738b15.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gather your friends and explore a variety of climbing gyms, each with unique routes. Collaborate to puzzle through tricky climbs, or compete for the best times in more dynamic routes.<br><br><br><strong>MADE FOR SPEEDRUNNERS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/e0049c4bf006e376519d94474a221336.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/e0049c4bf006e376519d94474a221336.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/e0049c4bf006e376519d94474a221336.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Designed for speedrunners, Tether has built-in timers for each route so you can continually challenge yourself. Find shortcuts, perfect your climbing, and shave off milliseconds to top the leaderboards!<br><br><br><strong>ADVENTURE MODE CHALLENGE</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/ae9fb6d279138b6ea3195c15d349d9a4.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/ae9fb6d279138b6ea3195c15d349d9a4.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/ae9fb6d279138b6ea3195c15d349d9a4.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Test your skills in Adventure Mode, a massive map that will have you trying again and again for the best time. Join with friends for moral support or compete in an ultimate race to the summit!",
  "about_the_game": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/fdb519eab434ceb0aeb905190b94b2bc.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/fdb519eab434ceb0aeb905190b94b2bc.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/fdb519eab434ceb0aeb905190b94b2bc.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to Tether, a world where chalk bags have arms and everything colorful is your personal playground. Its physics-driven movement system lets you play your way. Whether you like daring jumps, strategic climbs, or spinning in endless circles, the choice is yours!<br><br><br><strong>GRAB, CLIMB, SWING</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/a5ec056adff81c966a5fb284869e59e9.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/a5ec056adff81c966a5fb284869e59e9.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/a5ec056adff81c966a5fb284869e59e9.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tether isn’t your typical 2D platformer. There’s no running and jumping. Instead, master the art of grabbing, swinging, and flinging and climb your way to the top!<br><br><br><strong>EXPLORE WITH FRIENDS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/1134b04f399341e9f63cb9dedd738b15.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/1134b04f399341e9f63cb9dedd738b15.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/1134b04f399341e9f63cb9dedd738b15.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gather your friends and explore a variety of climbing gyms, each with unique routes. Collaborate to puzzle through tricky climbs, or compete for the best times in more dynamic routes.<br><br><br><strong>MADE FOR SPEEDRUNNERS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/e0049c4bf006e376519d94474a221336.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/e0049c4bf006e376519d94474a221336.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/e0049c4bf006e376519d94474a221336.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Designed for speedrunners, Tether has built-in timers for each route so you can continually challenge yourself. Find shortcuts, perfect your climbing, and shave off milliseconds to top the leaderboards!<br><br><br><strong>ADVENTURE MODE CHALLENGE</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/ae9fb6d279138b6ea3195c15d349d9a4.poster.avif?t=1725990518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/ae9fb6d279138b6ea3195c15d349d9a4.webm?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613510/extras/ae9fb6d279138b6ea3195c15d349d9a4.mp4?t=1725990518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Test your skills in Adventure Mode, a massive map that will have you trying again and again for the best time. Join with friends for moral support or compete in an ultimate race to the summit!",
